name: Self foot licking (anime)
description:
Well... the name speaks for itself.

Please use the following prompt to activate properly this lora :

1girl, close up, tongue out, saliva, soles, YOUR DETAILS, <lora>

Example : 1girl, close up, tongue out, saliva, soles, nurse, red eyes, hospital, <lora:selfFootLickingAnime_v10:0.6>

Tested on Anything v4.5 and Anyhentai, but it should work on most anime models. I suggest between 0.6 and 0.8 for the lora weight.

Since it was trained at 768x768 resolution, it seems to work much better if you generate at 768x768 (or 640x640 if you can't generate at higher resolution).

The pose is very specific so there isn't much room for variety.

Sample images setting :

  • Euler a

  • 24 steps

  • 768x768

  • Anyhentai model

  • Hires :

    • realESRGAN_4xplus_anime_6B

    • upscale by 1,5

    • denoising strength: 0,2

It's a work on progress so it can produce some weird results, but don't hesitate to share your images !
